ps://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-stairs-140525-153-10-1437x2048.jpg 1437w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe living spaces, perched higher on the bluff, are rewarded with sweeping ocean views, which pour into the interior through expansive floor-to-ceiling windows that define the home’s open layout. Natural light floods the warm and partially wood-clad interior, where clean lines and minimalist furnishings emphasize craftsmanship and comfort.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1249\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-11.jpg\" alt=\"Natural light floods the warm and partially wood-clad interior, where clean lines and minimalist furnishings emphasize craftsmanship and comfort.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-11.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-11-940x611.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-11-800x520.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-11-768x500.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-11-1536x999.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA sunken seating area with soft blue tones creates an intimate gathering space, while artful touches, like a sculptural wooden bench and abstract painting, add character without overwhelming the serene aesthetic.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1265\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-12.jpg\" alt=\"A sunken seating area with soft blue tones creates an intimate gathering space, while artful touches, like a sculptural wooden bench and abstract painting, add character without overwhelming the serene aesthetic.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-12.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-12-940x619.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-12-800x527.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-12-768x506.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-wood-stairs-140525-153-12-1536x1012.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA sleek, horizontal fireplace anchors the living room with minimalist elegance, its dark firebox contrasting the pale wall. Surrounded by sculptural furniture and soft tones, it serves as a refined focal point that blends warmth with modern coastal style.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2351\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-13.jpg\" alt=\"A sleek, horizontal fireplace anchors this living room with minimalist elegance, its dark firebox contrasting the pale wall. Surrounded by sculptural furniture and soft tones, it serves as a refined focal point that blends warmth with modern coastal style.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-13.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-13-940x1151.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-13-800x980.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-13-768x940.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-13-1254x1536.jpg 1254w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-13-1673x2048.jpg 1673w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1456\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-14.jpg\" alt=\"A sleek, horizontal fireplace anchors this living room with minimalist elegance, its dark firebox contrasting the pale wall. Surrounded by sculptural furniture and soft tones, it serves as a refined focal point that blends warmth with modern coastal style.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-14.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-14-940x713.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-14-800x607.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-14-768x582.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-living-room-fireplace-140525-153-14-1536x1165.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe layout of the home is composed of three distinct forms, which can be seen from the rear of the home. There’s a barn-like structure for the main suite and study, a granite-clad base embedded into the earth for guest and entertainment areas, and a glazed, transparent heart that houses the kitchen and social zones. This central core dissolves the boundary between indoors and out, allowing light, vegetation, and sea air to flow freely through the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.contemporist.com/?attachment_id=234140\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1265\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-design-architecture-140525-150-01.jpg\" alt=\"This modern home has three distinct levels to it, while outside, there\u0026#39;s a terraced backyard with swimming pool, outdoor kitchen, and pool house.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-design-architecture-140525-150-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-design-architecture-140525-150-01-940x619.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-design-architecture-140525-150-01-800x527.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-design-architecture-140525-150-01-768x506.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-design-architecture-140525-150-01-1536x1012.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOutside, a sequence of terraced platforms steps down to the swimming pool, echoing the site’s natural descent. Lush plantings and crisp stonework integrate the architecture with its hillside surroundings.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2087\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-landscaping-140525-152-15.jpg\" alt=\"This modern home has three distinct levels to it, while outside, there\u0026#39;s a terraced backyard with swimming pool, outdoor kitchen, and pool house.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-landscaping-140525-152-15.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-landscaping-140525-152-15-940x1226.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-landscaping-140525-152-15-800x1044.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-landscaping-140525-152-15-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-landscaping-140525-152-15-1178x1536.jpg 1178w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-landscaping-140525-152-15-1570x2048.jpg 1570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1864\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-16.jpg\" alt=\"This modern home has three distinct levels to it, while outside, there\u0026#39;s a terraced backyard with swimming pool, outdoor kitchen, and pool house.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-16.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-16-940x1095.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-16-800x932.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-16-768x895.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-16-1318x1536.jpg 1318w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWith panoramic ocean views as its backdrop, the lower terrace is anchored by an infinity-edge pool and flanked by generous lounge areas. A glass-walled pool house opens onto the terrace, while a built-in BBQ area nearby invites outdoor entertaining.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1265\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-17.jpg\" alt=\"With panoramic ocean views as its backdrop, the lower terrace of this modern house is anchored by an infinity-edge pool and flanked by generous lounge areas. A glass-walled pool house opens onto the terrace, while a built-in BBQ area nearby invites outdoor entertaining.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-17.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-17-940x619.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-17-800x527.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-17-768x506.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-swimming-pool-landscaping-140525-152-17-1536x1012.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003ePerched at the edge of the bluff, an intimate firepit lounge offers panoramic water views. Framed by low glass railings, the built-in seating creates a wind-sheltered retreat that blurs the line between comfort and coastline.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1271\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-outdoor-lounge-140525-152-18.jpg\" alt=\"Perched at the edge of the bluff, an intimate firepit lounge offers panoramic water views. Framed by low glass railings, the built-in seating creates a wind-sheltered retreat that blurs the line between comfort and coastline.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-outdoor-lounge-140525-152-18.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-outdoor-lounge-140525-152-18-940x622.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-outdoor-lounge-140525-152-18-800x530.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-outdoor-lounge-140525-152-18-768x508.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-outdoor-lounge-140525-152-18-1536x1017.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eBack inside, the dining room combines soft textures and natural materials for a relaxed, coastal feel. A sculptural wood table anchors the space, surrounded by upholstered chairs with warm wood frames. Sheer drapery filters the light, while woven pendant lights and a colorful abstract painting add layers of warmth and character.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1919\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-19.jpg\" alt=\"The dining room combines soft textures and natural materials for a relaxed, coastal feel. A sculptural wood table anchors the space, surrounded by upholstered chairs with warm wood frames. Sheer drapery filters the light, while woven pendant lights and a colorful abstract painting add layers of warmth and character.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-19.jpg 1919w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-19-940x1254.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-19-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-19-768x1025.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-19-1151x1536.jpg 1151w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-19-1535x2048.jpg 1535w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1919px) 100vw, 1919px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2086\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-20.jpg\" alt=\"The dining room combines soft textures and natural materials for a relaxed, coastal feel. A sculptural wood table anchors the space, surrounded by upholstered chairs with warm wood frames. Sheer drapery filters the light, while woven pendant lights and a colorful abstract painting add layers of warmth and character.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-20.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-20-940x1226.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-20-800x1043.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-20-768x1001.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-20-1178x1536.jpg 1178w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-dining-room-140525-151-20-1571x2048.jpg 1571w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTucked into corner of the open-plan living space, the breakfast nook with a built-in banquette creates an intimate dining zone.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1339\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/split-level-interior-140525-151-21.jpg\" alt=\"Tucked into corner of the open-plan living space, the breakfast nook with a built-in banquette creates an intimate dining zone.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/split-level-interior-140525-151-21.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/split-level-interior-140525-151-21-940x656.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/split-level-interior-140525-151-21-800x558.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/split-level-interior-140525-151-21-768x536.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/split-level-interior-140525-151-21-1536x1071.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAnchored by a pair of dramatic stone islands, the kitchen strikes a refined balance between natural warmth and sculptural elegance. Wood cabinetry wraps the space seamlessly, concealing appliances and enhancing the minimalist aesthetic.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1265\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-kitchen-140525-151-22.jpg\" alt=\"Anchored by a pair of dramatic stone islands, the kitchen strikes a refined balance between natural warmth and sculptural elegance. Wood cabinetry wraps the space seamlessly, concealing appliances and enhancing the minimalist aesthetic.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-kitchen-140525-151-22.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-kitchen-140525-151-22-940x619.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-kitchen-140525-151-22-800x527.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-kitchen-140525-151-22-768x506.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-wood-kitchen-140525-151-22-1536x1012.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA home bar anchors the far end of the open-plan living space, while open shelving niche showcases a curated display of ceramic vessels and glassware. A streamlined wooden pool table introduces a playful touch, complemented by a plush sofa and layered textures that lend the room a relaxed yet refined feel.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1328\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-23.jpg\" alt=\"A home bar anchors the far end of the open-plan living space, while open shelving niche showcases a curated display of ceramic vessels and glassware. A streamlined wooden pool table introduces a playful touch, complemented by a plush sofa and layered textures that lend the room a relaxed yet refined feel.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-23.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-23-940x650.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-23-800x553.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-23-768x531.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-23-1536x1062.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2087\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-24.jpg\" alt=\"A home bar anchors the far end of the open-plan living space, while open shelving niche showcases a curated display of ceramic vessels and glassware.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-24.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-140525-151-24-940x1226.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-home-bar-1